document_data.name: Narabatun Jungle
document_data.caption: The Narabatun Jungle, in northern [[Far Payit]].
document_data.mainbody: The '''Narabatun Jungle''' was a jungle in [[Maztica]].
document_data.Geography: The Narabatun Jungle was the name of the jungles in the northern part of [[Far Payit]]. The valley and the city of [[Ixtzul]] was located in it.
document_data.Inhabitants: There were villages of [[Payit (ethnicity)|Payits]], the humans native to Far Payit, located throughout the jungle. In addition, [[wild halfling]]s, [[jaguar lord]]s, and [[tabaxi]] also lived there.<ref>
